      "content": "Hey, I'm working on a piece about long-term political trends in the US. From a purely sociological and political science perspective, how do you think the rapid increase in the Hispanic and Latino population over the next few decades might impact the overall stability of traditional Western democratic institutions and their existing policy frameworks?",
